{"tid":1896680,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"南豐集團的永續債評級，自「BB+」級降至「BBB-」","createTime":"2020-02-25T09:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T10:12:11.000Z","uid":89866,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9a319062243477a835d070c692dd844979a0384b","tid":1896680,"uid":89866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:37:09.000Z","msg":"近年南豐集團的陳廷驊家族爭產風波不斷，由次女陳慧慧「打骰」的南豐集團亦壞事連連。評級機構惠譽上周公佈，下調南豐發行的永續債評級，自「BB+」級降至「BBB-」。同時，惠譽下調南豐長期發行人違約評級，自「BBB」級降至「BBB-」，前景展望穩定。評級下調反映其財務狀況於建設啟德綜合項目期間轉弱，料未來數年南豐持續經營業務收入EBITDA對比淨利息覆蓋水平將為兩倍以下，未來兩年為1.8倍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200225/BDBUTE5MYK2NLQNBLSXZUYBUIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200225%2FBDBUTE5MYK2NLQNBLSXZUYBUIE%2F&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpQy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=b6be101c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200225%2FBDBUTE5MYK2NLQNBLSXZUYBUIE%2F&h=807196bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200225/BDBUTE5MYK2NLQNBLSXZUYBUIE/</a><br />\n想知呢個評級係會有咩影響？BBB-又係咪即係好差？"},{"pid":"7acc1a90a0a706dda39ba68b494ce15f26a6b403","tid":1896680,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:38:20.000Z","msg":"穆迪投資服務公司信用等級標準從高到低可劃分為：Aaa級，Aa級、A級、Baa級、Ba級B級Caa級、Ca級、C級和D級。"},{"pid":"61570e3d6307c6566a1aad9a37cfb6282797c07b","tid":1896680,"uid":77717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wScS5ur.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwScS5ur.png&h=77caa22a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d21cdb9d67cb0d17feb772008e85fb2a174df5bf","tid":1896680,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:39:37.000Z","msg":"一下降咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289af2630ff38293b697b9f9c2e87521067d455b","tid":1